title: TOP 100 DANCE SONGS (1970-2008)
description:
As promised, I am back with my new compilation: TOP 100 DANCE COLLECTION.  Here is my list of the Top 100 Dance songs made between approx 1970 - 2008.  To give credit, most of these songs are from the posting by pctrecords entitled "100 Greatest Dance Hits Of The 90s."  I liked his list, but it was missing songs like Funkytown, Macarena, Play that Funky Music, and some others that weren't from the 90s but nevertheless felt left out of the original list.  I kept about 80 of his songs and added 20 of my own (including some awesome Gunther songs).  This is a much better list, trust me.  

I put these songs in order, too.  I apologize that this isn't a perfect list, but it's better than any else on the pirate bay currently.  I'm making TOP 100 Lists of all my different genres of music, and I'll have them posted shortly.  This is my second torrent that features Top 100 lists of different genres of music.
